sentence.text: In clinical practices, the therapeutic outcomes and prognosis of hepatocellular carcinoma (phosphatidylinositol phosphorylation) patients with different tumor numbers after surgery are very different; however, the underlying mechanisms of the tumorigenesis and development of HCC with different tumor numbers are still not well understood.
These information revealed that there might be different molecular mechanisms of the tumorigenesis and development of the phosphatidylinositol phosphorylation with single and multiple lesions.
